Bank of Israel to Impose New Limit on Mortgages, TheMarker Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   W r o b e l
-- 
2011-04-26T06:26:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/bank-of-israel-to-impose-new-limit-on-mortgages-themarker-says.html
The  Bank of Israel  will limit
mortgages to 40 percent of the value of a home from 60 percent
today, the financial daily TheMarker said, without saying where
it obtained the information. The measure is expected to be
announced as early as this week, possibly today, TheMarker
added.  Central bank spokesman Yossi Saadon said an announcement
can be expected in the coming days or beginning of next week.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
